{"tid":1265533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(全部人)一定一定要入黎答應我一樣野！","createTime":"2019-06-29T08:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T11:17:37.000Z","uid":260653,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21bb71be0afc4fc3f8bc92ec7a1880d5f04cd9ba","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"我知道大家好攰<br />\n我知道大家見到身邊既人善忘好心淡<br />\n我知道做左好多但都好似徒勞無功<br />\n好灰心好想放棄係咪？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喂醒未呀？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府就係想你地咁囉！</strong></span><br />\n想你地好似雨散革命咁<br />\n輸左就再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不聞不問</span></span></span><br />\n之後佢所有施政就一路順風<br />\n想dq邊個就邊個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">成個香港佢玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n <br />\n係呀政府以家係無野驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地最驚既係人民既堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n今次要大大力同政府講<br />\n我地唔會再犯同樣既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似雨革咁<br />\n兩個月就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家攰就抖<br />\n抖完就再黎<br />\n等佢唔好以為咁易磨滅到我地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條路好長<br />\n老土都要講句<br />\n堅持未必有成果<br />\n但唔堅持你就一定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以無論現階段贏定輸都好<br />\n希望大家一定要答應我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔準善忘</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">唔準好似雨傘之後咁<br />\n乜都扮睇唔到</span></span><br />\n一定要同呢個政府鬥長命<br />\n笑到最後先係贏家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我希望可以同大家一齊<br />\n笑到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>加油呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ea29b68784bd0878ffee89908044faf71a4448a5","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"fb5ace86715b5a48a65679a8f8bae0cf78a597b3","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed34746a3998e2324931f8fa209fbe49715d054","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c551e23d4b579ec998c2e9d596c255f465d44f0","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T09:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a1286719a7d4c4966fe96a8c1f56e3d93be2bc","tid":1265533,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike"